    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes methods of carrying Key Performance Indicators (KPIs) using the Network Service Header (NSH).  These methods may be used, for example, to monitor latency and QoS marking to identify problems on some links or service functions.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
